1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,860
<font size="20"><font color="#9dc2a9"><font size="13"><b>Saegusa Hospital</b></font></font></font>

2
00:00:07,490 --> 00:00:12,490
<font size="20"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><b><font size="15">{\an7}Wishes and Songs Will Be Heard</font></b></font></font>

3
00:00:11,560 --> 00:00:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's up, Soji?</font>

4
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something's off at Harmonia.</i></font>

5
00:00:14,770 --> 00:00:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No one's picking up the phone.</i></font>

6
00:00:17,070 --> 00:00:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they all went home?</font>

7
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No cell phone, no land line, nothing.</i></font>

8
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not normal.</i></font>

9
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll go back and check.</font>

10
00:00:25,890 --> 00:00:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>June is here, too.</i></font>

11
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's meet up in front of the office.</i></font>

12
00:00:38,990 --> 00:00:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

13
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this your doing?</font>

14
00:00:48,530 --> 00:00:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. It was a lady who's
 much scarier than me.</font>

15
00:00:53,090 --> 00:00:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So XENOS isn't playing around.</font>

16
00:00:56,580 --> 00:01:00,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's more like we've been 
going easy on you until now.</font>

17
00:01:00,630 --> 00:01:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I leave here if I defeat you?</font>

18
00:01:04,850 --> 00:01:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, I didn't create this space.</font>

19
00:01:09,670 --> 00:01:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But maybe...</font>

20
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you could get a tip or two if you do?</font>

21
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's more than enough.</font>

22
00:01:21,470 --> 00:01:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A calling arises from deep 
within in my burning heart</i></font>

23
00:01:26,470 --> 00:01:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's Show Time</i></font>

24
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The price of living in the time of freedom</i></font>

25
00:01:40,230 --> 00:01:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}"So, what do you want to do?"</i></font>

26
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just standing there with my empty body</i></font>

27
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:51,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like a calling to protect the world</i></font>

28
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I craved an unequaled gift</i></font>

29
00:01:58,370 --> 00:02:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lost in night's darkness</i></font>

30
00:02:01,470 --> 00:02:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until a voice called out to me</i></font>

31
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like the light that declares the dawn</i></font>

32
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll take you with me at 
any cost (I pray and wish)</i></font>

33
00:02:12,490 --> 00:02:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beyond the Echo-verse (To the future)</i></font>

34
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just being with you makes me strong</i></font>

35
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:19,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's not an exaggeration</i></font>

36
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That encounter was a supernova 
(Our eyes were locked)</i></font>

37
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In an instant, everything that I am 
(In an instant)</i></font>

38
00:02:25,690 --> 00:02:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Will be changed forever (Just to be)</i></font>

39
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A calling arises from deep
 within in my burning heart</i></font>

40
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

41
00:02:35,930 --> 00:02:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be who we are</i></font>

42
00:02:38,510 --> 00:02:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

43
00:02:41,050 --> 00:02:43,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be by your side</i></font>

44
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one's at the front desk.</font>

45
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Nagi? Was she inside?</font>

46
00:03:02,130 --> 00:03:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

47
00:03:03,620 --> 00:03:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we can't get in touch with μ, either.</font>

48
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's highly likely that Nagi 
was inside with her.</font>

49
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kyoya!</font>

50
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Off I go!</font>

51
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa?!</font>

52
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?!</font>

53
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?!</font>

54
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi, this way.</font>

55
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happening here?</font>

56
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is this?</font>

57
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's it going over there?</font>

58
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no good.</font>

59
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't take back control.</font>

60
00:03:57,300 --> 00:04:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like they have
 us right where they want us.</font>

61
00:04:01,990 --> 00:04:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch it, Nono-Ken!</font>

62
00:04:03,810 --> 00:04:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you doing over there?</font>

63
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, just in case 
when XENOS charges in...</font>

64
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't stop XENOS with that.</font>

65
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't say that like we're doomed!</font>

66
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll just do everything we can.</font>

67
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa?!</font>

68
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:26,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't half bad, miss.</font>

69
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're called Rui-san, am I right?</font>

70
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm surprised you know about 
the manager. I'm not even the talent.</font>

71
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think there's anyone else 
among XENOS who knows</font>

72
00:04:36,170 --> 00:04:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">more about Harmonia Entertainment than me.</font>

73
00:04:39,050 --> 00:04:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I'm what you call a "noob." 
I only got into it a few days ago.</font>

74
00:04:45,670 --> 00:04:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you mess with my talent.</font>

75
00:04:48,650 --> 00:04:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you think you're going to stall me?</font>

76
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't underestimate a former SI-VIS!</font>

77
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it, this doesn't make sense.</font>

78
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not even attacking us.</font>

79
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">XENOS, what are you trying to do?</font>

80
00:05:10,410 --> 00:05:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">μ...</font>

81
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry!</font>

82
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stick together, and there's 
nothing to be scared of!</font>

83
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we'll go home together, Nagi.</font>

84
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back to Kyoya!</font>

85
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm afraid it won't be that easy.</font>

86
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because our objective is—</font>

87
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, there!</font>

88
00:05:33,690 --> 00:05:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This takes me back, old man!</font>

89
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:38,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one attacked us, so I felt lonely.</font>

90
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, now! SI-VIS girls 
are quick to lose their temper—</font>

91
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess the secondary form has its limits.</font>

92
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">μ! I'll help you now!</font>

93
00:05:51,030 --> 00:05:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now, Medea.</i></font>

94
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Nagi!</font>

95
00:06:10,090 --> 00:06:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Oh, boy.</font>

96
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might get yelled at for this later.</font>

97
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm.</font>

98
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Front and back entrances, 
second-floor window,</font>

99
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">underground parking lot, it's all bust.</font>

100
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We get tossed out.</font>

101
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does this mean the whole building 
is covered in the Mirage?</font>

102
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a different type of 
application than we've seen,</font>

103
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm sure it's similar technology.</font>

104
00:06:39,710 --> 00:06:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, aren't they...?</font>

105
00:06:43,710 --> 00:06:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do we get inside?</font>

106
00:06:45,930 --> 00:06:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To connect with the Mirage,</font>

107
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:50,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we need the backstage stuff and the staff.
 Both are inside the building.</font>

108
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Metis as well.</font>

109
00:06:52,580 --> 00:06:57,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means that right now, we have 
no way of connecting with the Mirage.</font>

110
00:06:58,060 --> 00:06:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

111
00:06:59,650 --> 00:07:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, how about what we did when we jumped 
out of the helicopter the other day?</font>

112
00:07:04,210 --> 00:07:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't your power.</font>

113
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hayama-san said it was Nagi-chan's power.</font>

114
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:10,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right!</font>

115
00:07:11,030 --> 00:07:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Nagi's also trapped 
in here, we can't use it.</font>

116
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we can use it!</font>

117
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was inside and I was 
outside of the Mirage back then.</font>

118
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we just need to do the same.</font>

119
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were able to touch 
Nagi directly at back then.</font>

120
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, we don't 
even know where she is.</font>

121
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then there's nothing we...</font>

122
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:32,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just need to deliver it.</font>

123
00:07:33,210 --> 00:07:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our location to her!</font>

124
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, what is your purpose?</font>

125
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't even start to guess 
what kind of technology you use,</font>

126
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I can tell the difference 
in its strength.</font>

127
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I hate to admit it, but I can tell 
that you're holding back on me, too.</font>

128
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no, I did go all-out.</font>

129
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I'm running multiple 
applications, this is my limit.</font>

130
00:07:58,350 --> 00:08:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, it's true that I'm personally
not interested in killing you right away.</font>

131
00:08:04,710 --> 00:08:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because that'd be</font>

132
00:08:06,350 --> 00:08:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">boring, you know?</font>

133
00:08:10,050 --> 00:08:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Isn't this...</font>

134
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the server room?</font>

135
00:08:15,350 --> 00:08:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was only going to lure in the diva.</font>

136
00:08:23,260 --> 00:08:26,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I guess this is within 
the margin of error.</font>

137
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Attacking without even
hearing what I have to say?</font>

138
00:08:32,830 --> 00:08:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so barbaric!</font>

139
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the invader 
who attacked out of nowhere,</font>

140
00:08:36,380 --> 00:08:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I don't want to hear it!</font>

141
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">μ!</font>

142
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weren't invited here 
in the first place.</font>

143
00:08:46,340 --> 00:08:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please sit there and be quiet.</font>

144
00:08:50,590 --> 00:08:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi... run.</font>

145
00:09:03,070 --> 00:09:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one with the blood 
of Eden the Diva.</font>

146
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

147
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Medea.</font>

148
00:09:10,350 --> 00:09:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to this planet 
to tell you the truth.</font>

149
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the record 
your friend left behind.</font>

150
00:09:22,470 --> 00:09:24,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, a video?</font>

151
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yosuke and Nagi? What is this?</font>

152
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you're not surprised.</font>

153
00:09:34,610 --> 00:09:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi?</font>

154
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow... Somehow I knew it.</font>

155
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I wasn't like Kyoya and μ.</font>

156
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. You are one of us.</font>

157
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a member of the tribe 
those around you shun as "invaders."</font>

158
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Orphe is as well.</font>

159
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the XENOS you all called "Yosuke."</font>

160
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the one who betrayed us, kidnapped 
you, and brought Earth into this war.</font>

161
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the main culprit.</font>

162
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You named the diva "Nagi," 
and you never told her who she was.</font>

163
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never told the members 
of SI-VIS who Orphe was.</font>

164
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you were afraid 
that it would sever their bond,</font>

165
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and SI-VIS would fall apart.</font>

166
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was only looking for 
the right time to tell them.</font>

167
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, they were too young 
and immature to bear this secret.</font>

168
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

169
00:10:42,570 --> 00:10:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a sensitive subject.</font>

170
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I get where you're coming from.</font>

171
00:10:48,190 --> 00:10:54,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But right now, your indecisiveness 
will be our advantage.</font>

172
00:10:55,410 --> 00:10:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The diva will probably feel that 
you betrayed her, you know?</font>

173
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And SI-VIS won't be able to accept 
the truth about Orphe, you know?</font>

174
