<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it a clone, an artificial child, 
or a mix of both?</font>

345
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyhow, that's what gave birth to Nagi.</font>

346
00:20:29,870 --> 00:20:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's altered, but still a child of hope 
who has the blood of Lady Eden.</font>

347
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I found out that truth,</font>

348
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he pointed his blade at me 
and hid everything away.</font>

349
00:20:47,630 --> 00:20:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea. Do you remember 
what I said back then?</font>

350
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:55,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doubt everything.</font>

351
00:20:55,220 --> 00:20:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not believe everything easily.</font>

352
00:20:57,620 --> 00:21:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doubt, doubt, and doubt it even more.</font>

353
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And only believe in the truth 
that's left in the end.</font>

354
00:21:03,870 --> 00:21:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope that the truth you arrive at 
will be the same one I found.</font>

355
00:21:10,810 --> 00:21:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let Apollo steal Nagi away.</font>

356
00:21:14,560 --> 00:21:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She may be able 
to save both of my homes.</font>

357
00:21:25,850 --> 00:21:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your wish... 
I was finally able to receive it.</font>

358
00:21:32,070 --> 00:21:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... if possible, please be aliv—</font>

359
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, man. Well, that was a failure.</font>

360
00:21:39,780 --> 00:21:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They totally gave me the slip.</font>

361
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had no choice.</font>

362
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We misjudged SI-VIS's... 
no, humans' relationships of trust.</font>

363
00:21:49,870 --> 00:21:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us retreat.</font>

364
00:21:51,380 --> 00:21:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry back and ask 
for instructions from Lord Apollo—</font>

365
00:21:54,420 --> 00:21:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, wrong answer.</font>

366
00:21:57,910 --> 00:22:03,570
